            <div type="transcript" id="F341A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>'Tis so appalling - it exhilirates -</l>
                    <l>So over Horror, it half captivates - </l>
                    <l>The Soul stares after it, secure - </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="To know the worst, leaves no dread more -">A Sepulchre, fears frost,  no more -</add>
To know the worst, leaves <app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 no dread more -</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To scan a Ghost, is faint -</l>
                    <l>But grappling, conquers it - </l>
                    <l>How easy, Torment, now - </l>
                    <l>Suspense kept sawing so - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Truth, is Bald - and Cold - </l>
                    <l>But that will hold -</l>
                    <l>If any are not sure - </l>
                    <l>We show them - prayer - </l>
                    <l>But we, who know, </l>
                    <l>Stop hoping, now - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Looking at Death, is Dying -</l>
                    <l>Just let go the Breath -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>And not the pillow at<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 your cheek </l>
                    <l>So slumbereth - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Others, can wrestle - </l>
                    <l>Your's, is done -</l>
                    <l>And so of Wo, bleak dreaded -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 come, </l>
                    <l>It sets the Fright at liberty - </l>
                    <l>And Terror's free - </l>
                    <l>Gay, Ghastly, Holiday!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
